job.title: IBPS CRP Clerk XI Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 5830 Vacancies in India
job.body:
Total vacancies:5830

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Common Recruitment Process (CRP) 

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for Graduates have been published by the Institute of Banking Personnel Selection for Common Recruitment Process vacancies in India. If you are searching for a government job in India then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Common Recruitment Process, from 12-07-2021 and till 01-08-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in India and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about the application fee

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Common Recruitment Process in IBPS, your Graduation must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 12-07-2021
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 01-08-2021

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 35 years old. 

IBPS Common Recruitment Process Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

How to apply for IBPS CRP Clerk XI Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Common Recruitment Process. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of IBPS and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by IBPS
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
